â”‚# Kubernetes Security Tools Installation

## kube-bench
https://github.com/aquasecurity/kube-bench

Run:
kube-bench run

---

## kubescape

Install:
curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kubescape/kubescape/master/install.sh | /bin/bash

Run:
kubescape scan framework nsa

---

## trivy

Install:
brew install trivy

Run:
trivy image nginx
